Name: Average time from 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE' to 'Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE' and activity 'Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR'

Name: Average time between 'Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR' and 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR' and activity 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE'

Name: Total resolution time of 'Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR'
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR and the end of the case

Name: Average waiting time to the 'Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR' after 'Declaration FOR_APPROVAL by SUPERVISOR'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration FOR_APPROVAL by SUPERVISOR' and activity 'Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR'

Name: Minimun time from 'Declaration FOR_APPROVAL by SUPERVISOR' to 'Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR'
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Declaration FOR_APPROVAL by SUPERVISOR' and activity 'Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR'

Name: Average time it takes 'Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR' after 'Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION' and activity 'Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR'

Name: Total time for 'Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR' to be followed by a new 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE'
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR' and activity 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE'

Name: Minimun resolution time of 'Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR' in cases leading to 'Request Payment'
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR' and activity 'Request Payment'

Name: Time from 'Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR' to 'Declaration APPROVED by PRE_APPROVER' in the re-submission process
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR' and activity 'Declaration APPROVED by PRE_APPROVER'

Name: Average time for 'Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR' in cases where 'Declaration APPROVED by BUDGET OWNER' follows
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR' and activity 'Declaration APPROVED by BUDGET OWNER'

Name: Total time since 'Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR' until 'Payment Handled' in successful cases
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR' and activity 'Payment Handled'

Name: Average time to re-submit after 'Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR' before 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR' and activity 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE'

Name: 'Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR' Cycle Time in comparison to 'Declaration APPROVED by SUPERVISOR' Cycle Time
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR' and activity 'Declaration FINAL_APPROVED by SUPERVISOR'
